docs {
  ## Update Product Category
  อัปเดตข้อมูลหมวดหมู่สินค้าที่มีอยู่

  Modifies an existing product category, such as renaming it or adjusting its display order.

  ### Path Parameters
  - `id` — Product Category UUID (รหัสหมวดหมู่สินค้า)


  ### Sample Body
  ```json
  {
    "name": "",
    "code": "",
    "is_active": true
  }
  ```

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "uuid",
      "message": "Success"
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 200,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-03-27T00:00:00.000Z"
  }
  ```
}

